				\begin{document}$$d(i,j)=\sqrt{{({x}_{i}-{x}_{j})}^{2}+{({y}_{i}-{y}_{j})}^{2}+{({z}_{i}-{z}_{j})}^{2}}$$\end{document}d(i,j)=(xi−xj)2+(yi−yj)2+(zi−zj)2
